A–C) by the wider bulb and from those of 
<taxonomicName id="46DCD9FFFF3CCEECFD7FFC3FD9B03829" authorityName="Rios-Tamayo &amp; Goloboff" authorityYear="2018" box="[640,739,1006,1032]" class="Arachnida" family="Actinopodidae" genus="Actinopus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="177" pageNumber="178" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ariasi">
